sentences: Shaun Charles Frank (born June 7, 1982) is a Canadian DJ, singer-songwriter and record producer.
The Envy opened for KISS in 2010 on their Hottest Show on Earth Tour.
In 2016, Frank co-wrote the chart-topping single "Closer" by The Chainsmokers.
2014: Kiesza – "Take Me to Church" (Shaun Frank Remix)
